  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Gravity Area Weapons project <span class=3DSpellE>gr=
avitic</span>
  vortexes at specific points in space. The center of the vortex is some
  distance away from the firer. The <span class=3DSpellE>gravitic</span> vo=
rtex
  pulls nearby ships inwards and inflicts enormous vibrational damage as th=
ey
  come closer.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Gravity Area weapons have quite high power requireme=
nts,
  and thus are usually found only on larger military ships or larger bases =
like
  space ports or defensive platforms.</p>
